<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-84-0642 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper discusses a technique of design for a Flywheel-CVT-transmissionsystem to drive an industrial forklift. The design procedure is generaland can be applied to automobiles or trucks. Component system characteristicsnecessary to perform the design task are presented and discussed. Resultsshow the advantage of this system for industrial, military and food processingindustries.</TEXT></DOC>